Package: idps
Title: Identification and Description of Precipitation Systems (idps)
Version: 0.0.0.9
Authors@R: 
    person("Ahmed", "Homoudi", , "ahmed.homoudi@tu-dresden.de", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-6906-5986"))
Description: The package uses object-based methods combined with a tracking 
algorithm to utilise the GPM_3IMERGHH (V06) data set to identify and describe 
precipitation systems. 
